    <item>
      <title>阿根廷将在平行市场抛售美元以支撑比索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-13/argentina-to-sell-dollars-in-parallel-fx-market-caputo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷央行将从周一开始在平行货币市场抛售美元，以支撑比索。今年迄今为止，比索的非官方汇率已贬值逾 30%，进一步加剧了通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-13/argentina-to-sell-dollars-in-parallel-fx-market-caputo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 16:28:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
